data.description: 2.75% Assumable Rate! Remarkable Two-bedroom, two-bath with a Den!  located within a coveted guard-gated community This exceptional end-unit townhome distinguishes itself by offering an unmatched level of privacy - a rarity for a townhome - as it stands without shared walls, ensuring tranquility and convenience! Experience modern comfort through a multitude of recent upgrades, including new quartz kitchen counters, fresh paint, ambient cabinet lighting, and bespoke storage solutions. All appliances, including the washer and dryer, have been updated in the last two years. The AC unit and water heater were also replaced within the last three years, ensuring extra peace of mind. High ceilings amplify the living spaces, while a gas fireplace adds an elegant touch as the grand center piece of the home.  The master suite indulges with dual closets, backyard access, and a newly remodeled bathroom featuring a bench-equipped shower and chic farmhouse accent. Schedule a viewing today!
